cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.MM 

This paper is about object detection, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of attention mechanisms (cs.AI) and introduces a new backbone architecture (cs.LG) to improve efficiency and accuracy. Additionally, the paper addresses the use case of real-time detection (cs.RO) and compares the proposed method to a popular real-time detector (cs.MM).
